import React from 'react';
import {Container,Grid,Box,styled,Paper,CardMedia,useMediaQuery,useTheme} from '@mui/material';
import Navbar from './Navbar';
import headerjpg from '../assets/headerImage.png'
import BgImg from '../assets/bgnew.jpg'
import Designjpg from '../assets/dBg.png'
const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1A2027' : '#fff',
    ...theme.typography.body2,
    padding: theme.spacing(1),
    textAlign: 'center',
    color: theme.palette.text.secondary,
  }));

function Header(props) {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const isMatch = useMediaQuery(theme.breakpoints.down("md"));
    return (
      
        <React.Fragment>
                <Navbar/> 
                {/* <Paper sx={{ backgroundImage: `url(${BgImg})`,
    backgroundRepeat: 'no-repeat',backgroundSize: 'cover'}} > */}
      <Container maxWidth={false} disableGutters  sx={{}}>
 
      <Box  sx={{ flexGrow: 1,
      backgroundColor:'#222222',
        // background: 'rgba(0.0,0.0,0.0,0.7)'
        }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
      <Grid  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  alignItems="center"
  justifyContent="center"item xs={3} lg={4}>
   
    <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1',color:'#fff',position: 'absolute',
    top: '28%',
    fontSize: 100,
    /* width: 0px; */
    left: '19%',
    zIndex: 0}}>Arun</Box>
     <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1',color:'#f16b50',position: 'absolute',
    top: '43%',
    fontSize: 100,
    /* width: 0px; */
    left: '8%',
    zIndex: 0}}>kumar</Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  alignItems="center"
  justifyContent="center" item xs={6}  lg={3}>
        <CardMedia
        component="img"
        sx={{ 
          // width: '100%',
        height:isMatch?'auto': 600 ,
        zIndex: 1,
        position: "relative"}}
        image={headerjpg}
        alt="Live from space album cover"
      />
        </Grid>
        <Grid   container
  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  justifyContent="center"
  style={{padding:'20% 0% 0% 2%'}} item xs={6} lg={5}>
     <CardMedia
        component="img"
        sx={{ 
          // width: '100%',
        height:isMatch?'auto': 100 ,
        zIndex: 1,
        position: "relative"}}
        image={Designjpg}
        alt="Live from space album cover"
      />
          <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption',color:'#ef6a4f' }}>Senoir Programmer</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'h3',color:'#fff'  }}>Based in India,I'am Front End Developer</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' ,color:'#fff' }}>Worked as front end developer with 5+ year experience on  web and mobile development</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption',color:'#ef6a4f',marginTop:2}}>9994334040</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption',color:'#ef6a4f' }}>jk23arunkumar@gmail.com</Box>
        </Grid>
      
      </Grid>
    </Box>
    
        </Container>
        {/* </Paper> */}
<Container>
        <Box  sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid   container
  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  alignItems="center"
  justifyContent="center"
  style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6} lg={6}>
          <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
      </Grid>
      </Grid>
      </Box>
      </Container>
      <Container>
        <Box  sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid   container
  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  alignItems="center"
  justifyContent="center"
  style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6}>
          <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
      </Grid>
      </Grid>
      </Box>
      </Container>
      <Container>
        <Box  sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid   container
  spacing={0}
  direction="column"
  alignItems="center"
  justifyContent="center"
  style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6}>
          <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
      <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
      </Grid>
      </Grid>
      </Box>
      </Container>
        </React.Fragment>
    );
}

export default Header;
